{
  "stem": "6777.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But a coincidence of out-- out of all the workers' camps and out of all the peoples of different nationalities sent to the camps, these two kids came together again.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He corresponds with her even now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I needed a certificate, she gave it to me, only recently.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the uprising, I've been in Warsaw itself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was another Jewish man, also in the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in the proper army, though he came across to me with his rifle on his back and gave me all the information, because I have not been in the shooting, so to say, army.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have been in the one which have just been gathering information.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, the arising has died out, because Polish and Russian Army on the other side of the Vistula wouldn't come in while there was still a Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They waited till the Germans have finished off so that the Polish communist government could take over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people who survived have been marched out of the city into one of the stations-- railway stations past Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the railway station of Warsaw itself, the three railway stations, have been flattened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, and while we've been marched out, I skipped away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was towards evening, and there was a highway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on both sides of the highways have been ditches, fairly deep ditches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I hopped into one of those ditches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Out of the ditch and into a building, which turned out to be a bakery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this bakery has been supplying bread and rolls and all sort of things to the local villages-- not local, the surrounding villages, and, among other villages, the one where my sister and grandma and Eva and Mina have been.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
